title: Miss Seiling wins Cinderella crown (Northwestern Oklahoma State University)
text: ( Source : Northwestern Oklahoma State University ) October 9, 2015 Jasmine Seevers, Miss Seiling , walked away with the title of Miss Cinderella in the 64th annual Miss Cinderella Pageant at Northwestern Oklahoma State University, Friday.
